{"id": 1023, "genre": 1001, "title": "在睡觉这件事情上，你有哪些作作的习惯？", "description": "睡前仪式一大堆，稍不顺心就睡不着，新时代的豌豆公主，我。（题图来自：Thomas Hedger）", "record_count": 8296, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183948emhqbuRVA1ZJyLOC.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-01T11:00:40Z", "options": [{"id": 94464, "content": "曾经是必须侧睡必须右侧", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632190}, {"id": 94720, "content": "每次出门都不知道穿什么好……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664735}, {"id": 184064, "content": "听音乐电台定时，早起被耳机缠住?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983263}, {"id": 264961, "content": "绝对安静", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260940}, {"id": 265985, "content": "侧睡，不穿袜子，听一会儿音乐，看一会儿书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164187}, {"id": 94465, "content": "裸睡、前提是在家里", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652329}, {"id": 94721, "content": "一定要侧着睡，而且必须背对窗才睡的着！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145926}, {"id": 97793, "content": "非要确定门锁没有，然后一定要上个厕所，确定手机已经充好电，然后才睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152720}, {"id": 94466, "content": "现在是必须不起夜，有也忍着", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632190}, {"id": 94978, "content": "睡前来一发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643918}, {"id": 94467, "content": "怕热，绝对保证凉快才能睡好。怕声音吵，必须关房间门。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 497445}, {"id": 94723, "content": "摸自己的胸睡....", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664715}, {"id": 101635, "content": "睡前把床铺平整把枕头摆正", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690802}, {"id": 94468, "content": "睡前一定要上厕所，一定要保持安静和黑暗，所以眼罩和耳塞是我的睡眠好伴侣，一定要靠右睡?", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652947}, {"id": 94724, "content": "右侧卧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664708}, {"id": 184068, "content": "必须戴耳塞 完全黑暗\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923358}, {"id": 94469, "content": "虽然半夜很少醒来喝水，但是水杯里必须有70%的水", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664016}, {"id": 94725, "content": "一定要开小灯碎觉，被子会捂住来睡 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 262662, "content": "手放裤裆里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081151}, {"id": 265734, "content": "不盖被子难受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266363}, {"id": 283398, "content": "一定要关机才睡得着，已经养成习惯了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351961}, {"id": 94470, "content": "睡前聽聽歌或者看一下視頻。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308060}, {"id": 94982, "content": "确认躺倒在床上的时候，没有压到我的小贱猫", "image": "img/option/option/20160703152305DwO31IKCNmEGgqBd.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653303}, {"id": 104198, "content": "睡觉之前手机调静音", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 94471, "content": "必须露出脚丫，一年四季如此", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664019}, {"id": 178183, "content": "眼睛困了，但玩手机的心不困", "image": "img/option/option/20170313103612le0AaUKTgwb1qD5P", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968481}, {"id": 94472, "content": "只睡自己认定的床，一张床从家搬到学校再搬回来我会乱说？", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641054}, {"id": 94728, "content": "一定要翻完手机看完所有动态再睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664754}, {"id": 94473, "content": "睡觉必须穿袜子", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655562}, {"id": 292105, "content": "喜欢这样睡.......", "image": "img/option/option/20180711223024IXz87corhNPMwaWy.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391192}, {"id": 178185, "content": "不能听到一点声音，周围必须静静的，不然睡不着。", "image": "img/option/option/20170313103840ev0DCHqG1J7N2Izn", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968481}, {"id": 94474, "content": "抱点什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573447}, {"id": 173066, "content": "一定不能压着左心脏，即使醒的时候各种姿势\n一定要用被子把自己裹好，即使半夜因为踢被子冻醒...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817672}, {"id": 262923, "content": "上厕所 喝水 累到玩不动手机了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238268}, {"id": 94475, "content": "睡前深深的吸一口气", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664040}, {"id": 230923, "content": "无论天气有多么热，睡觉时总要被子盖住全身，要不心里不舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111150}, {"id": 94476, "content": "睡觉的时候必须安静，除了极端想睡觉那种情况。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664043}, {"id": 94732, "content": "没什么特别的仪式，大部分情况下沾枕头就着。??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664753}, {"id": 94477, "content": "必须要有抱枕。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663400}, {"id": 94478, "content": "很窗户外面的小女孩打招呼晚安", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664047}, {"id": 94734, "content": "睡前要刷牙", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333327}, {"id": 174606, "content": "以前必须要平躺才能睡着\n不过现在不知道怎么回事开始侧身睡了\n哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957757}, {"id": 94479, "content": "骑被子", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334297}, {"id": 94735, "content": "侧睡腿夹个东西随便啥  只要夹着就舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654554}, {"id": 292879, "content": "睡觉的时候肚皮上一定不能有东西挨着！衣服被子什么的也不行，否则就觉得自己在感受自己的呼吸一起一伏，，，睡不着……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378892}, {"id": 317711, "content": "脱了的衣服必须要叠好挂好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1521608}, {"id": 262416, "content": "谁都不能弄脏我的床，穿着睡觉得衣服不能坐客厅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249355}, {"id": 94480, "content": "必须抱着一个玩偶，实在没有抱枕头或者被子", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621871}, {"id": 292880, "content": "睡觉的时候肚皮上一定不能有东西挨着！衣服被子什么的也不行，否则就觉得自己在感受自己的呼吸一起一伏，，，睡不着……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378892}, {"id": 94481, "content": "腿要夹着被子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78417}]}